               <scopecontent id="aspace_3c7dd85e4fc33cbe72832b01bfa88c4d">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Laid in at the front of the volume are:
- Two sheets denoting the translation of Joseph von Chlingensberg auf Berg's cipher
- A makeshift envelope, contemporary, that contains a letter from "Therese" (two bifolia and a single leaf) addressed to Joseph von Chlingensberg auf Berg.</p>
                  <p>Laid in throughout are notes (not contemporary).</p>
               </scopecontent>
