               <scopecontent id="aspace_04f6ed52c7c9341d24dee6c9a573bff0">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>While it is the same Schrieb-Kalender as every other volume (except 1803), this volume is in a paperback binding.</p>
                  <p>This volume is encrypted with a cipher created by Joseph von Chlingensberg auf Berg.</p>
                  <p>Notes from contemporary and later sources are laid in throughout, some with decoded passages of the diary.</p>
               </scopecontent>
